|5   |Collapse occurs                        |Single eigenvalue emerges  |
|6   |Single state manifests                 |Classical outcome          |
|7   |State evolves classically              |Classical dynamics continue|

**Completion Assessment:** 行 pillar = 100% complete for Possibility stage

Operation is not incomplete. Unitary evolution perfectly executes the Possibility stage’s internal dynamics. Measurement-induced transition perfectly executes the boundary passage to Existence.

